abstract: Baseball Roundup; Chicago Cubs beat Cleveland Indians, 2-1; other baseball results noted.
lead_paragraph: Kris Bryant hit a home run with two outs in the ninth inning as Chicago topped Cleveland in a makeup game from a June 15 rainout.

headline.main: Cubs Win Fifth Straight With Help of Rookie’s Walk-Off Homer
headline.print_headline: Cubs Win Fifth Straight; Braves End a Seven-Game Slide
